data.description: Introducing your ideal residence nestled within the esteemed 12 Oaks community of Holly Springs! Upon entry, the intricate craftsmanship captivates with moldings and trim work accentuating each corner, harmonized by coffered ceilings lending an air of refinement throughout. The main level unfolds with lustrous hardwood flooring, fostering a cozy and welcoming atmosphere.    Central to the home, the expansive kitchen and family room area epitomize modern elegance with contemporary tile accents and abundant space for both gatherings and daily life. The chef-inspired kitchen boasts premium appliances, a sizable island, and a convenient butler's pantry/dry bar, ensuring an unparalleled cooking experience. Adjacent, a screened porch overlooks the tranquil patio and fenced yard, offering a serene outdoor escape.    Convenience meets luxury with a first-floor bedroom accompanied by a full bath, perfect for guests or multi-generational living. Upstairs, the oversized primary suite beckons with dual closets and a lavish en-suite bathroom for ultimate comfort and rejuvenation. Three additional bedrooms cater to family and guests, while a third-floor bonus room presents versatile possibilities and ample storage.  12 Oaks provides an abundance of amenities including golf, pickleball, tennis, a swim club, and fitness facilities, ensuring endless avenues for leisure and recreation.  Seller is offering a 2/1 buy down with the preferred lender.
